    <div id="articleView">
        <div id="articleTop" style="font-family: NanumGothic;">
            <p class="title">벤, 정확한 슬픔의 발라더 </p>
            <p class="stitle"><월간 채널예스> 2019년 1월호 </p>
            <div class="snsList">
                <ul>
	<li><a href="javascript:SNSToPostOpen('facebook', 650, 300);" title="페이스북"><img src="http://image.yes24.com/images/chyes24/content/images/btn/btn_fb.gif" alt="페이스북" /></a></li>
    <li><a href="javascript:SNSToPostOpen('twitter', 600, 250);" title="트위터"><img src="http://image.yes24.com/images/chyes24/content/images/btn/btn_tw.gif" alt="트위터" /></a></li>
